title: Baidu Terminates $3.6B Deal to Buy JOYY's China Live-Streaming Business
description: Baidu has called off a $3.6 billion deal to buy JOYY’s video-based entertainment live-streaming business in China saying certain conditions were yet to be fully satisfied.

title: Big Tech Braces for Wave of Antitrust Rulings in 2024
description: U.S. antitrust cases against tech giants Google and Meta are expected to come to a head, likely producing long-awaited rulings that could shape the legacies of top Biden administration regulators.
